/responses and stubs.\",\n    \"The native-image failure shown for 2.0-beta4 appears related to version-specific behavior in existing tests, not missing external infrastructure.\",\n    \"A logging binding is optional only; slf4j-api is resolved through the artifact dependencies, and lack of a binding should not block meaningful coverage.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0aa2a768646e6a36016a41f3d9bf888197bc85dc486d74dd06\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 3985, "output": 1321, "cacheRead": 29184, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 34490, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782707144070, "responseId": "resp_0aa2a768646e6a36016a41f3c8aca88197b6faaa19c3913d4d"}, "toolResults": []}
